spirit:parameter.spirit:name: axiProtocol
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter axiProtocol sets the AXI protocol type.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: cacheLineSize
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Define cache line size in Bytes. Only used for ACE_LITE/ACE5_LITE/ACE5_LITE_DVM cache maintenance and cache stashing support.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: enRead
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter enRead is set to True, the AR and R channels are enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: enWrite
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter enWrite is set to True, the AW, W and B channels are enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: mmuVersion
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Version of AXI Untranslated transactions support.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: signalNameFormat
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Format of AXI signal names. Binary encoding, handled by SW.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useAtomic
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useAtomic is set to True, support for Atomic access is enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useBigEndian
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useBigEndian is set to True, big endian is used on the AXI-Lite socket.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useCacheStashing
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useCacheStashing is set to True, support for Cache Stashing is enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useFixed
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useFixed is set to True, support for FIXED burst access is enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useMmuATST
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useMmuATST is set to True, the Ax_MmuATST ports are present.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useMmuFlow
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useMmuFlow is set to True, the Ax_MmuFlow ports are present and the R_Resp/B_Resp ports are extended to support TRANSFAULT.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: useUniqueId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: When parameter useUniqueId is set to True, support for Unique ID indicator is enabled.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wAddr
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wAddr sets the address field field of the AR and AW channels.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wData
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wData sets the data field width of the R and W channels.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wDataInfo
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wDataInfo sets the DataInfo bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wId sets the ID field width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wLen
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wLen sets the Len bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wLoop
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wLoop sets the Loop bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wMmuSId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wMmuSId sets the Ax_MmuSId bits width and, if is greater than0, the presence of the Ax_MmuSecSId.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wMmuSSId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wMmuSSId sets the Ax_MmuSSId bits width and, if is greater than0, the presence of the Ax_MmuSSIdV.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wQos
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wQos sets the Qos bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wRegion
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wRegion sets the Region bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wReqUser
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wReqUser sets the request user bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wRspUser
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wRspUser sets the response user bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wStashLPId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wStashLPId sets the Aw_StashLPId bits width and, if is greater than0, the presence of the Aw_StashLPIdEn.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wStashNId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wStashNId sets the Aw_StashNId bits width and, if is greater than0, the presence of the Aw_StashNIdEn.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wUTId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wUTId sets the UTId bits width.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: wVMId
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Parameter wVMId sets the VMId bits width.
